@ENDNODE
@NODE HISTORY "History"

      Version
    * 0.0    - Original version written for me.

    * 0.1    - fixed bugs in the way the button fits in the window.  First public release.

    * 0.2    - Added tooltypes to allow people to change the CD device and unit.

    * 0.3    - Added tooltypes to allow people to change the window positions.

    * 0.4    - Added tooltypes to allow people to change the window title,  button text, fontname,
    fontheight and the ability to centre the window.

@ENDNODE
